Description_lang: Goroth selects a target and then hurls a $@spellname233272 at them after $233272d1, inflicting $s1 Fire damage to all enemies within $A1 yards. This damage is decreased by every Infernal Spike the $@spellname233272 collides with.If the $@spellname233272 collides with no Infernal Spikes, the target is ignited, suffering $236329s1 Fire damage every $236329t1 sec for $236329d.Any other targets struck by the $@spellname233272 while it is traveling to its target take $233281s1 Fire damage.
